Title: Dora the Explorer: Dora Saves the Mermaids

reviewText: I actually like Dora for my kids. Its not "scary" it does not have good vs evil themes with villains. It does not have romantic themes, and is generally pretty innocent with no bad attitude or anything I wouldn't want my kids to pick up from a TV show or movie.I also do catch my kids saying a few spanish words here and there. And this particular one does appeal to my daughter who is really into mermaids right now.
summary: My kids love it, and that's what counts!
